    <h2>Is it harmful (human activity) foam?</h2>

    <ul>
      <li><strong>Causes:</strong> could be excess phosphorus in the water</li>
      <li><strong>Colour:</strong> usually white</li>
      <li><strong>Smell:</strong>  fragrant, perfumed or soapy</li>
      <li><strong>Area:</strong> usually occurs over small area, localized near source of discharge</li>
    </ul>

    
